# 🔐 SecureVault

A modern password management application built with **React**, **TypeScript**, and **Vite**. SecureVault provides a clean and intuitive interface for storing and managing credentials while demonstrating modern frontend development practices.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔑 Secure credential management
- 📱 Responsive design
- ⚡ Fast performance with Vite
- 🎨 Modern UI/UX
- 🔒 TypeScript-powered reliability
- 🧩 Reusable React components

